@node history "History"
v1.2 (8th June 1999) Marc Christiansen reported that the bug mentioned below was
still present, only this time it didn't appear until the 2245th number. I have
adjusted the program, now all numbers should be the correct length.
v1.1 (7th March 1999) Fixed a bug that caused numbers after the 150th number to
appear too short. Now they are the correct length.
v1.0 (25th April 1998) First public release.
@endnode
